Package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.datalake

Class DataLakeResourceManager

java.lang.Object
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.git.GitDataRetriever<DataLakeFile>
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.datalake.DataLakeResourceManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataRetriever<GitFile,DataLakeFile>
public class DataLakeResourceManager extends GitDataRetriever<DataLakeFile>
A Manager/Retriever for Files for which indicator files are stored in the git Repository. Each Repository that contains resources will be represented by one folder in the datalake which will contain all data.
Author:
thomas
